lyrics:
In the depths of my mind, a crematorium lies,
Burning all my feelings, beneath its fiery skies.
Living vulgarly within, afraid of what I'll find,
Lost in my own thoughts, trapped in my own mind.

(Chorus)
My mind is a crematorium, burning emotions bright,
Scorching all my fears, engulfing me in light.
Living within myself, afraid of what I see,
Lost in this inferno, trying to break free.
